# Newsletter signup — Resend Audiences
# These power the /api/subscribe server route, which adds an email to the
# "razbakov.com newsletter" Resend Audience. They are SERVER-ONLY (wired through
# nuxt.config.ts runtimeConfig, never exposed to the client). Nuxt maps the
# NUXT_-prefixed env vars onto runtimeConfig.resendApiKey / resendAudienceId.
#
# Get the API key from https://resend.com/api-keys (account-wide key works).
# Get the audience id from https://resend.com/audiences (or create one via
# POST https://api.resend.com/audiences with {"name":"razbakov.com newsletter"}).
NUXT_RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
NUXT_RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
